All right, Frank.
A $10 loan, plus
two dollars' interest,

573
00:47:15,233 --> 00:47:18,503
plus 50-cents-a-day
late penalty, uh...

574
00:47:18,569 --> 00:47:20,906
Screw off, Dickie.

575
00:47:30,882 --> 00:47:34,319
I think it's time
for a young man...

576
00:47:34,385 --> 00:47:38,323
