summer for Kidco.
Mm-hmm.

594
00:48:57,969 --> 00:49:02,273
As a matter of fact,
we're thinking of getting
into communications.

595
00:49:02,340 --> 00:49:05,276
So if someone wanted
to ask me on a date,

596
00:49:05,343 --> 00:49:08,479
and they just so happened
to be a newspaper man,

597
00:49:11,249 --> 00:49:14,185
