your lovely sisters
with you.

619
00:50:56,087 --> 00:50:59,124
Well, we've got
a pretty full schedule,

620
00:50:59,190 --> 00:51:01,058
but I think we could
stop in for a minute.

621
00:51:01,126 --> 00:51:03,228
Good.

622
00:51:07,598 --> 00:51:10,835
